## Button\
\
Buttons are interactive elements that trigger actions when clicked or tapped. They guide users through workflows, initiate processes, and can alter the state of a given experience.\
\
## Anatomy\
\
[Figma UI Kit Reference](https://www.figma.com/design/LqnpoHfyFAXDJpZsOeunLP/Coefficient-UI-Kit?m=auto&node-id=7283-47618&t=GuylrMzcAsh1OVLT-1)\
