## Figma UI Kit\
\
Coefficient maintains a SAP-specifc UI kit that combines the SAP-specific components, variables, and settings with Coefficient's design tokens, allowing designers and developers to work directly with SAP components and properties without the friction of an additional translation step to convert designs to their SAP equivalents.\
\
Get the [UI Kit here](https://www.figma.com/design/Pu3zyWEc5VhI5Ccmbfe1fM/SAP-Fiori-for-Web-UI-Kit?node-id=2-8&t=R9SpG7zDPfez4w3V-1) and please use it as your base when creating designs for SAP Fiori applicaitons.\
\
