\
In addition to solid colors, a set of approved background textures is available provided by Creative Services. These can be used in place of the background color to add visual depth while maintaining the standard slot structure. You may find links to the most up to date textures in the assets section of the [Branding](/docs/coefficient/fundamentals/brand.md#assets) documentation.\
